title: Sound On: Dems Eco Agenda Delayed to 2022
itunes:title: Sound On: Dems Eco Agenda Delayed to 2022
description:
Guests: Nadeam Elshami, former Chief of Staff to House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi and policy director at Brownstein, Hyatt, Farber and Schreck, White House Council of Economic Advisers chair, Cecilia Rouse, Doug Heye, Republican Strategist, and former Deputy Chief of Staff for former House Majority Leader Eric Cantor and Bloomberg politics contributor Jeanne Sheehan Zaino.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
